Rover Technical Test

Description 

This project processes sitter reviews from a CSV file and computes ranking scores for each sitter.

The program:

- Loads reviews from a CSV file

- Groups reviews by sitter

- Computes three scores for each sitter:

   Profile score 
   Ratings score
   Search score

- Sorts sitters based on the computed search score

- Generates a final CSV file containing the ranked sitters

Requirements

Node.js >= 18

npm

Installation:

npm install

Running the project

To run the program:

npm run start

The program will:

Load the reviews from the input CSV file (/files/initial/reviews.csv)

Compute sitter scores

Sort sitters by search score

Generate an output file named:

sitters.csv (/files/result/sitters.csv)